messages.message:
Devmode looks cool (https://www.figma.com/dev-mode/), I’m not sure how much better it is vs. our current workflow but I’m willing to give it a try!

That being said, it seems like we’d need to request access for a seat. Considering how uh, frugal, we are with seats, we’d have to get a LOT of value to offset the headache of requesting seats.
But perhaps we can request access from IT just to test it out? Assuming we have some designs to go with it.
